markov-java project: poem generator 

Hidden Markov Model second-order: frequency of word pairs describes probability of possible next words, then chosen by comparing probability to random number. 

Input file: text file containing various song lyrics, differnt genres for diversity. 

A longer input file generates "better" results (less repetitive output, more instances of unique outputs compared to the input file).


Output: generates 10 lines of a new poem/nursery rhyme